         <div type="translation" resp="#jmr" xml:lang="en">
            <p> To Lucius Septimius Geta Caesar <note>all erased</note> son of emperor Caesar Lucius Septimius Severus Pius Pertinax Augustus, victor in Arabia, victor in Adiabene, greatest victor in Parthia, and brother of emperor Caesar Marcus Aurellius Antoninus Augustus, Messius Atticus, first priest, paid his vow.</p></div>
